    "long_instructions": "## Video Game Developer - Level 1: Zero-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice zero-shot prompting through the career of a video game developer by giving a simple, unstructured prompt to see how AI creates dialogue without any examples or guidance.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a basic prompt like the one below, or a similar one related to character conversations.\r\n\r\n>Write a conversation between a hero and a villain.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how interesting, creative, or repetitive the dialogue is.",
